<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Your CIBIL Score & Loan Offer</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", Arial, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f4f7f9;
            color: #333;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .email-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            background: #ffffff;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4c75fe, #1e50d8);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4c75fe, #1e50d8);
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(76, 117, 254, 0.4);
        }
        .btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3a5fcc, #163ea5);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #7d7d7d;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>Your Loan Application</h1>
            </div>
            <h2>Hello {{template_content.customer_name}},</h2>
            <p>Your CIBIL score is: <strong>{{template_content.cibil_score}}</strong></p>
            <p>Based on your score, you are eligible for a loan of â‚¹{{template_content.loan_amount}}.</p>
            <p>Your credit rating: <strong>{{template_content.credit_rating}}</strong></p>
            {{!-- <a href="{{template_content.form_link}}" class="btn">Proceed with Application</a> --}}
            <div class="footer">
                <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:voiceopsacp@gmail.com">voiceopsacp@gmail.com</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
